At character creation, characters have a 0 in all attributes.
At character creation, a player receives points which they may spend on improving their attributes.
Commonly, a player has 6 points to spend, the costs of scores are as follows;
+1 costs 1 Point
+2 costs 2 Points
+3 costs 4 Points
+4 costs 8 Points
+5 costs 16 Points
Inversely, a player may give a character negative scores in Attributes, this gives them more points to spend on other Attribnutes.
-1 gives 1 Point
-2 gives 2 points
-3 gives 4 Points
-4 gives 8 Points
